@startuml Builder Pattern
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF

title Builder Pattern - Type-Safe Mediator Construction

package "Builder Hierarchy" {
    
    abstract class "ReportingMediatorBuilder" as BaseBuilder {
        + buildComponents()
        + buildReceivers()
        + buildSenders()
        + buildSchedulers()
        + buildFlows()
        + {abstract} createBroker()
        + {abstract} createSerializer()
    }
    
    package "RW Builders" {
        class "KafkaJsonRWBuilder" as KafkaJsonRW {
            + createBroker() : KafkaBroker
            + createSerializer() : JsonSerializer
        }
        
        class "KafkaProtobufRWBuilder" as KafkaProtobufRW {
            + createBroker() : KafkaBroker
            + createSerializer() : ProtobufSerializer
        }
        
        class "RabbitMQJsonRWBuilder" as RabbitMQJsonRW {
            + createBroker() : RabbitMQBroker
            + createSerializer() : JsonSerializer
        }
        
        class "RabbitMQProtobufRWBuilder" as RabbitMQProtobufRW {
            + createBroker() : RabbitMQBroker
            + createSerializer() : ProtobufSerializer
        }
    }
    
    package "Exclusive Builders" {
        class "KafkaJsonExclusiveBuilder" as KafkaJsonExcl
        class "KafkaProtobufExclusiveBuilder" as KafkaProtobufExcl
        class "RabbitMQJsonExclusiveBuilder" as RabbitMQJsonExcl
        class "RabbitMQProtobufExclusiveBuilder" as RabbitMQProtobufExcl
    }
}

BaseBuilder <|-- KafkaJsonRW
BaseBuilder <|-- KafkaProtobufRW
BaseBuilder <|-- RabbitMQJsonRW
BaseBuilder <|-- RabbitMQProtobufRW

BaseBuilder <|-- KafkaJsonExcl
BaseBuilder <|-- KafkaProtobufExcl
BaseBuilder <|-- RabbitMQJsonExcl
BaseBuilder <|-- RabbitMQProtobufExcl

class "Director" as Director {
    + construct(builder)
}

class "ReportingMediator" as Mediator {
    - components
    - flows
    - broker
    - serializer
}

Director -right-> BaseBuilder : uses
Director -down-> Mediator : creates

note right of BaseBuilder
  **Template Method Pattern:**
  - Base class defines algorithm
  - Subclasses provide specifics
  - Compile-time type safety
end note

note bottom of Director
  **Director ensures:**
  - Correct build order
  - All steps executed
  - Validation
  - Consistent construction
end note

note left of Mediator
  **Result:**
  - Fully configured mediator
  - Type-safe
  - All components wired
  - Ready to run
end note

note as N1
  **Complete Matrix:**
  4 mediator types × 2 brokers × 2 serializers
  = 16 total builders
  
  All combinations fully implemented!
end note

@enduml
